Subject: Journalism Today
Description: Are Independent websites taking over media magazine audiences? Where should new journalists start and how is Traditional Journalism changing?  Join Junkhead Josh Jankiewicz (Hardcore Gaming 101) Ay-hole Andy (blahblahmusic .com) and veteran journalists Erica McClain and Dave Herndon as they share their experiences and tips about Journalism.  Speakers include:'Ay-hole' Andrew Zelasko, 'Junkhead' Joshua Jankiewicz, David Herndon, Erica McClain - Track: Media  - Duration: 50 minutes - Audio/video needs: none
